making peanut brittle.

263
00:10:11,367 --> 00:10:13,752
Ooh. Try some.

264
00:10:13,836 --> 00:10:15,488
Ooh.

265
00:10:15,572 --> 00:10:17,123
No eating
in the hospital.

266
00:10:17,207 --> 00:10:20,392
Um, so, Erika, it looks like
you have some bleeding

