269
00:10:25,748 --> 00:10:27,949
Alright, page me
when she's ready, Schmitt.

270
00:10:29,719 --> 00:10:31,370
I won't tell
if you won't.

271
00:10:35,684 --> 00:10:41,437
And I know we've only
