275
00:10:49,939 --> 00:10:51,223
I mean,
I heard you were tough,

276
00:10:51,307 --> 00:10:53,874
but I didn't think
you were cold.

277
00:10:56,613 --> 00:10:58,631
I want you closer.

278
00:10:58,715 --> 00:11:00,533
