500
00:20:34,924 --> 00:20:37,624
<i>But you are
Amelia Shepherd.</i>

501
00:20:39,495 --> 00:20:41,146
<i>So you got this.</i>

502
00:20:59,148 --> 00:21:01,333
What's she doing?

